<HTML><BODY>
This Perl module makes the use of clearprompt(1) both simpler and more
portable between UNIX and Windows.  It handles UNIX/NT quoting and path
issues transparently, manages creation, reading, and deletion of temp
files in text/list/file modes, and adds a clearprompt_dir() function to
prompt for a directory.  Note: a newer version may be present at
<A HREF="http://www.perl.com/CPAN-local/modules/by-module/IPC/DSB/">
http://www.perl.com/CPAN-local/modules/by-module/IPC/DSB/</A>.
</BODY></HTML>
